</select>


<p>You also gain the Bardic Inspiration ability, which you can use as a bonus action. It allows you to choose a creature that can hear you within 60 feet, and it gives that creature a Bardic Inspiration Die (six sided die). Within the next ten minutes, it can use that die once to add the number on it to an ability check, attack roll, or saving throw. You can use this ability as many times as your Charisma modifier, and you regain uses of it after every long rest.</p>
